<body>
    <div class="bg-container d-flex flex-column justify-content-end">
        <div class="advanced-technologies-card"></div>
        <h1 class="advanced-technologies-title"> Advance Technology</h1>
        <p class="advanced-techonologies-descripton">Machinery and equipment develope from the application of scintific knowledge.</p>
